snippet.title: ASHEN | E3 2017 Rebirth Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming soon to Xbox and PC. http://www.ashen-game.com/

Xbox: http://bit.ly/AshenXbox
Epic: http://bit.ly/AshenEpic
Steam: http://bit.ly/AshenGameSteam

Ashen is an action role-playing game about a wanderer in search of a place to call home. This is a world where nothing lasts, no matter how tightly you cling to it. At its core, Ashen is about forging relationships. Players can guide those they trust to their camp — together, you might just stand a chance.

Developed by AURORA44. Published by Annapurna Interactive.

© Annapurna Interactive, 2017
